							<span class="index">1</span>
							<div class="text">
								<span>国内或西班牙境内由专业老师进行选择指导语言学校</span>
							</div>
						</div>
						<div class="item">
							<span class="index">2</span>
							<div class="text">
								<span>帮助填写语言申请表，并进行语言学校注册</span>
							</div>
						</div>
						<div class="item">
							<span class="index">3</span>
							<div class="text">
								<span>协助汇款以及跟踪汇款</span>
							</div>
						</div>
						<div class="item">
							<span class="index">4</span>
							<div class="text">
								<span>邮寄录取通知书</span>
							</div>
						</div>
